data.text: @hellomag Wonder how how it took for her to scream inside.. I’m a celebrity, get me out of here !!!  I know I would be cracking in the middle of all that !!
@hellomag Like other Germans, the Royal Family open their gifts on Christmas Eve. Do you think they took any of Meghan’s traditions to make her feel included? Rice and peas? Jerk Chicken? Homophobia?
